content.rendered:
Directed by Nissam Basheer

Written by Sameer Abdul

Cast Mammootty (Luke Antony). Grace Antony (Sujatha). Jagadish (Head Cost. Ashraf). Bindu Panikkar (Seetha Balan). Sharafudheen (Satheeshan). Kottayam Nazeer (Shashankan). Sanju Sivram (Anil Balan). Asif Ali (Dileep Balan). Mani Shornur (Balan). Ira Noor (Sophia Luke). Sreeja (Sujatha’s Mother (as Sreeja Ravi)). Keerikkadan Jose (Sujatha’s Father). Priyamvada Krishnan (Ammu). Zeenath (Satheeshan’s Mother). Mathew Mampra (Rasheed – Robber’s Father). Nilambur Ayisha (Sainaba – Robber’s Mother). Jordi Poonjar (Insp. George). Babu Annur (SI P. Pisharody). Naji M Baji (Adv. Joseph). Asha (Kabani). S. George (Luke’s Advocate). Riyas Narmakala (Babu). Geethi Sangeetha (Hospital Nurse). Ravi Pattena (Police Constable 1). Sagar Sathyan (Police Constable 2). Gilu Joseph (Police Constable 3). Usha Chandra Babu (Police Constable 4). Muhammed Siraj (Dr. Chandran). Shajie Naduvil (Murali).Aneesh Shoranur

Languages Malayalam

Producers Mammootty

Production Mammootty Kampany. Wayfarer Films
